>\n3. 但部機又無真係shut down，個power制閃閃下<br />\n4. 無blue screen，又唔知邊度有得睇error log，想知多少少個問題係咩都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"我都係win10 更新咗唔知D咩野. 最近係咁開唔郁. 好鬼煩<br />\n一係黑屏 但有燈. 一係就藍屏<br />\n成日次次突然hang 機之後 重新開返都話自己更新咗D咩野懶威咁. 真係好鬼嬲<br />\n我仲以為係硬件壞. 想砌過部新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd1b3be758a9051f19fe0345ae62ace7ccca6af","tid":2439614,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f457eeecc1581fd3ad727c49be3df64f3fc93f9f","tid":2439614,"uid":276592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"再補充：<br />\n因為係播片就出事，所以唔知係咪同display card有關？<br />\nNVIDIA GeForce GTX 1080<br />\n岩岩見二月尾有driver update，我試下update睇下會唔會好D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"我上星期都有hang機問題<br />\n又係update過gpu driver<br />\n依家還原左去460.79就冇事"},{"pid":"f9d4e43f55253981219dff59b5f43d4a86e9bbb1","tid":2439614,"uid":149012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd1b3be758a9051f19fe0345ae62ace7ccca6af","tid":2439614,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f457eeecc1581fd3ad727c49be3df64f3fc93f9f","tid":2439614,"uid":276592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"再補充：<br />\n因為係播片就出事，所以唔知係咪同display card有關？<br />\nNVIDIA GeForce GTX 1080<br />\n岩岩見二月尾有driver update，我試下update睇下會唔會好D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"我上星期都有hang機問題<br />\n又係update過gpu driver<br />\n依家還原左去460.79就冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"請問. 係咪過咗唔知幾多日就無得還原上一個更新點?"},{"pid":"67ae7870b48f602e72dc88d5c3a24347f345139e","tid":2439614,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d4e43f55253981219dff59b5f43d4a86e9bbb1","tid":2439614,"uid":149012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd1b3be758a9051f19fe0345ae62ace7ccca6af","tid":2439614,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{